Cargo Park is a highly desirable business park suited to transport and logistics users with unrivalled exposure to the Tullamarine Freeway. Smart traffic planning and an expansive internal hardstand allows for excellent b-double access and truck movement. This recently refurbished business park provides a fantastic corporate presence as well as unrivalled access to major infrastructure and local amenity.
